mb - too. Yes. Ribs, you know. I've had that for a shilling. Brisket, the price it is today, I've had a big piece of brisket, as a queen could have eaten, when I was married, when I was married to him, oh not by me first husband, by him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10306935 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16718425\charrsid10703177 But when you were at school meat was rare?
