 confide in - really at all because - I knew what they'd they'd been with me and - they never tried to - encourage me to get on, you know I mean? I'd got the chances and chances.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10306935 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16718425\charrsid10703177 So you feel your parents expected obedience from you?
