Not once. 'Cos me father didn't believe in God. He didn't. And he worked in the pit, but he never believed in God, he always said as there wasn't - there wasn't God.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10306935 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16718425\charrsid10703177 Were you taught to say your prayers at night?
