y used to - pick. See every so often you - you were moved from the class into another class, going up. Same as they do now. And - me - down. And they picked - not - well - perhaps there was some in that class - as hadn't - were going up, same as me not go
ing up in - and then she'd - you - you - you - you. You'll go in - Miss so and so's class. See? I'd stay down. But I was just the same, I couldn't learn nothing nor - I couldn't.
