 hat on. Me feet have been - oh, cold you know. So this woman across the road, her girl - was in the same class as me. I knew her. She were nice girl. And - her mother - opened the curtain and - I - I was looking across see but I couldn't see in the house
,
 but I was looking that road because - the steps was facing the window you see. And in she goes. She beckoned me across and I - I looked and I thought to myself, well it nobody else about, she must mean me. I went across. She said - you're a lot early. We
