. You had any breakfast? Yes. What have you had? I said, I've had a piece of bread and jam. Had a cup of tea? I said, no. Well which I hadn't. So - she gave me - I - I remember it, bacon and egg. Who she'd cooked it for I don't know but she didn't have ti
