nd - I pushed one penny down one stocking and one penny - down the other. And I told me - oh - this girl - I've forgot her name, but any road, the girl - she brought - a parcel, and there was some clothes in it. Shoes. Well - they were good shoes. And you
 
won't believe this but my mother pawned 'em. She really did. Well - I couldn't say anything about the shoes because - I knew what I should have got. And this woman - well - she didn't bother with me after. Because she could see - she give me these clothes
 
