 - oh not me, they didn't - they would - they wouldn't have me with 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10306935 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16718425\charrsid10703177 You felt that you were left out of things?
